  {title_en: "news", title_ch: "最新消息", content: "                        \r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                                                \r\n                        <h1 class=\"title\">最新消息</h1><hr><br><br><ul>針對產護護理相關正面新聞報導。</ul>\r\n\r\n                        \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n                        \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n                        \r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n                        \r\n\t\t\t\t\t", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "service", title_ch: "服務內容", content: "<h1 class='title'> 服務內容 </h1><hr><br><br> <p1>※服務目標： <br>一、本著「全心」、「全意」的理念與宗旨，關懷住民及家屬。 <br>二、本著專業知識，提供專業化人性化有尊嚴的關懷和照護。</p1> <p2><br><br>※服務理念： <br> 一、全心：讓您感覺貼心、讓您感覺安心、讓您感覺放心。 <br> 全意：讓顧客滿意、讓員工得意、讓全體如意。 <br> 二、產婦及新生兒應有被呵護的月子生活。 <br> 三、尊重毎一位住民的個性與自主性。 <br> 四、尊重毎位住民的隱私權。 <br> 五、宗教信仰給人精神上的寄託，尊重毎位住民的宗教信仰。 <br> 六、員工要經常接受專業訓練，以提升專業照護品質。 <br> 七、耐心聆聽及婉轉回答，視毎一位住民為自己的親屬。 <br> 八、環境專業化並鼓勵住民家屬參訪，使住民有家的感覺。 <br> 九、讓毎位住民有健康的身體。 <br> 十、適當的安排各項活動使住民的身心獲得舒解及安適。</p2> <p3><br><br>※本產後護理之家特色介紹<br><br><br> 馥御產後護理之家位於台北市大安區微風商圈，捷運出口3分鐘，生活機能佳。<br>附設廚房，每餐提供熱騰騰營養料理。<br>資深護理人員24小時照護媽媽與寶寶，專業照顧一級棒。<br>特約資深小兒科與婦產科醫師定期診視。<br>定期舉辦媽媽教室提供衛教課程。<br>全區室內建材採防火低甲醛綠建材，合格消防設施與消防通道。<br>每房專屬電動擠乳器<br></p3>", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "environment", title_ch: "環境介紹", content: "<h1 class=\"title\">環境介紹</h1><hr><br><br> <div class=\"col-md-12 col-xs-12 envi_content\"> <div class=\"col-md-3 col-xs-3 envi_list\"> <ul> <li class=\"envi_list_title\">服務中心</li> <li class=\"envi_list_title\"><a href=\"e-nursestation.html\">護理站</a></li> <li class=\"envi_list_title\"><a href=\"e-babyroom.html\">嬰兒室</a></li> <li class=\"envi_list_title\"><a href=\"e-classroom.html\">媽媽教室</a></li> <li class=\"envi_list_title\"><a href=\"e-counter.html\">衛教諮詢室</a></li> <li class=\"envi_list_title\"><a href=\"e-spa.html\">SPA/洗頭室</a></li> </ul> </div> <div class=\"col-md-9 col-xs-9 envi_img\"> <div class=\"rooms_b\"> <img height=\"272\" id=\"big\" name=\"big\" src=\"/assets/img/A-C3.jpg\"> </div> <ul class=\"rooms\"> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/0824-C1.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/0824-C1_small.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/A-C2.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/A-C2.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/A-C3.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/A-C3.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/0824-C2.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/0824-C2_small.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/0824-C3.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/0824-C3_small.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> <li class=\"rooms_s\" onmouseover=\"document.images.big.src='/assets/img/0824-C4-1.jpg'\"> <img class=\"envi_pic_s\" height=\"63\" src=\"/assets/img/0824-C4-1_small.jpg\" width=\"100\"> </li> </ul> </div> </div>\r\n", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "rooms", title_ch: "房型介紹", content: "<h1 class=\"title\">房型介紹</h1><hr><br><br><p>房型介紹</p> <ul class=\"in_right\"> <li class=\"col-md-9 col-md-offset-3 col-xs-9 col-xs-offset-3 photo_frame\"><a href=\"room1\"><img height=\"120\" src=\"/assets/img/0824B-C1_small.jpg\" width=\"187\"> <br> <span class=\"room_name\">VIP房</span></a> </li> <li class=\"col-md-4 col-md-offset-3 col-xs-4 col-xs-offset-3 photo_frame\"><a href=\"room2\"><img height=\"120\" src=\"/assets/img/0824B-C2_small.jpg\" width=\"187\"> <br> <span class=\"room_name\">尊爵房</span></a> </li> <li class=\"col-md-4 col-xs-4 photo_frame\"><a href=\"room3\"><img height=\"120\" src=\"/assets/img/room_1_small.jpg\" width=\"187\"> <br> <span class=\"room_name\">典雅房</span></a> </li> </ul> \r\n", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "medteam", title_ch: "醫療團隊", content: " <h1 class='title'>醫療團隊</h1><hr><br><br> <p1> <div class='doctor_title'>婦產科醫師○○○ 醫師</div> 學歷: ○○○醫學系畢業<br> 經歷: ○○○婦產科主治醫師<br> ○○○科臨床講師<br> ○○○醫院婦產科主任<br> 現任: ○○○婦產科診所 院長<br><br> <div class='doctor_title'>小兒科醫師○○○ 醫師</div> 經歷: 前○○○醫院小兒科主治醫師<br> 前○○○醫院新生兒科主任<br> 中華民國小兒科專科醫師<br> 中華民國新生兒科專科醫師<br> 現任: ○○○診所院長<br> 負責人許慧英 護理師<br> 學歷: ○○○○護理系畢業<br><br> <div class='doctor_title'>兒童發展師</div> 經歷:榮總護理長?年以上經驗<br> 產後護理集團副督導<br> 產後護理集團護理長<br><br> <div class='doctor_title'>產後運動訓練師○○○ 老師</div> 學歷: ○○○○醫技系<br> 國體運動保健科學所運動傷害防護組<br> 經歷: 醫檢師<br> 現任: 大○○○○運動中心指導老師<br> 大產後瘦身指導老師<br><br> </p1>", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "meal", title_ch: "月子餐", content: "<h1 class=\"title\">月子餐</h1><hr><br><br> <p class=\"descriptions\"> 委託專業月子餐料理提供每餐熱騰騰新鮮料理，並延請營養師提供營養諮詢，媽媽吃得健康又開心。<font color=\"#FF0000\">(紅字問Vivian)<br> 1. 早餐：米漿/牛奶/豆漿，中西式混合搭配主菜，青菜及附菜<br>2. 調養飲品：杜仲枸杞補腎茶/補氣養肝茶/窈窕塑身茶/元氣紅棗養血茶/強健補血歸耆茶/杜仲枸杞補腎茶/補氣養肝茶<br>3. 午餐：湯，主菜，附菜，青菜，飯，水果<br>4. 午點甜品：銀耳紅棗蓮子湯/酒釀芝麻湯圓/紫米紅豆桂圓粥/花生圓仔湯/沖繩老薑地瓜湯/銀耳桂圓湯/養身八寶粥<br>5. 晚餐：湯，主菜，附菜，青菜，飯，水果<br>6. 養身燉品：驅寒麻油雞腿盅/十全排骨強身湯/發奶花生豬腳盅/杜仲枸杞補腎明目子排盅/暖身麻油豬肝腰內肉盅/十全補身燉雞盅<br></font>※參考菜單表(一周七天為橫軸，三正餐二點心為縱軸排列)<br> </p> <ul class=\"enlarge\"> <!--We give the list a class so that we can style it seperately from other unordered lists--> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/brown_rice.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"brown_rice\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/brown_rice.jpg\" alt=\"brown_rice\"> <!--popup image--> <br>十榖飯 <!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/red_bean_rice.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"red_bean_rice\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/red_bean_rice.jpg\" alt=\"red_bean_rice\"> <!--popup image--> <br>紅豆飯<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/red_rice.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"red_rice\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/red_rice.jpg\" alt=\"red_rice\"> <!--popup image--> <br>紅槽飯<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/pork_chop.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"pork_chop\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/pork_chop.jpg\" alt=\"pork_chop\"> <!--popup image--> <br>彩椒豬腳<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/fish.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"fish\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/fish.jpg\" alt=\"fish\"> <!--popup image--> <br>魚<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/chicken_soup.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"chicken_soup\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/chicken_soup.jpg\" alt=\"chicken_soup\"> <!--popup image--> <br>雞<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/vegetables.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"vegetables\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/vegetables.jpg\" alt=\"vegetables\"> <!--popup image--> <br>新鮮食蔬<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/kidney.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"kidney\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/kidney.jpg\" alt=\"kidney\"> <!--popup image--> <br>腰子<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/lotus_soup.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"lotus_soup\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/lotus_soup.jpg\" alt=\"lotus_soup\"> <!--popup image--> <br>蓮子銀耳湯<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/sesame_chicken.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"sesame_chicken\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/sesame_chicken.jpg\" alt=\"sesame_chicken\"> <!--popup image--> <br>麻油雞<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/pig_liver.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"pig_liver\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/pig_liver.jpg\" alt=\"pig_liver\"> <!--popup image--> <br>豬肝<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/herbs_1.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"herbs_1\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/herbs_1.jpg\" alt=\"herbs_1\"> <!--popup image--> <br>藥膳<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/herbs_2.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"herbs_2\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/herbs_2.jpg\" alt=\"herbs_2\"> <!--popup image--> <br>藥膳2<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/rice_porridge.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"rice_porridge\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/rice_porridge.jpg\" alt=\"rice_porridge\"> <!--popup image--> <br>糯米粥<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li> <img src=\"/assets/img/liver_soup.jpg\" width=\"250px\" height=\"166px\" alt=\"liver_soup\"> <!--thumbnail image--> <span> <!--span contains the popup image--> <img src=\"/assets/img/liver_soup.jpg\" alt=\"liver_soup\"> <!--popup image--> <br>養肝湯<!--caption appears under the popup image--> </span> </li> <li></li> </ul>\r\n", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "babycare", title_ch: "寶寶照護", content: "<h1 class='title'>寶寶照護</h1><hr><br><br><ul>馥御產後護理之家提供產後至滿月的寶寶照護，<br>包括新生兒身體評估，臍帶護理，母乳哺餵，<br>沐浴清潔，黃疸檢測等等。<br>嬰兒室獨立動線設計並附隔離區，避免院內交叉感染。<br>特聘資深小兒專科醫師及護理人員定期巡診及專業照護<br> </ul>", category: "main", parent: "none"},
  {title_en: "mommycare", title_ch: "媽咪照護", content: "<h1 class='title'>媽咪照護</h1><hr><br><br> <ul>馥御產後護理之家提供產後至滿月的媽媽照護，包括傷口護理，乳房護理，<br>母乳哺餵，餐食提供，營養指導與新生兒照護指導等等。<br><br> 特聘資深婦產科專科醫師定期巡診及專業照護。<br> 特聘資深瑜珈老師授課，指導媽媽產後骨盆運動，調整體態，快樂迎接新生命到來。<br> </ul>", category: "main", parent: "none"},
